  "description": "<p>Have work experience with private projects for 3 to 5 years</p>\n<p>To carry out site supervision and inspection of the works to ensure the works are constructed to required quality and accuracy</p>\n<p>Supervision &amp; Inspection for bore piling, ERSS, earth retaining  wall &amp; precast work with approved dwg, specification, rule &amp;  regulation.</p>\n<p>Monitoring in structural material test and checking Method Statements, tests and drawings</p>\n<p>Work closely with Consultants, Client &amp; authority and attend progress and technical meetings</p>\n<p>Reply some RFA/RFI and Maintain updated drawings/RFA/ RFI, all site records</p>",
